qNL: How many business rates are related to each cmi cross reference? List cross reference id, master customer id and the n
true_SQL: SELECT T2.cmi_cross_ref_id ,  T2.master_customer_id ,  count(*) FROM Business_Rates AS T1 JOIN CMI_Cross_References AS T2 ON T1.cmi_cross_ref_id  =  T2.cmi_cross_ref_id GROUP BY T2.cmi_cross_ref_id
qSQL: SELECT CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id, CMI_Cross_References.master_customer_id, COUNT(Business_Rates.business_rates_id) AS n FROM CMI_Cross_References LEFT JOIN Business_Rates ON CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id = Business_Rates.cmi_cross_ref_id GROUP BY CMI_Cross_References.cmi_cross_ref_id, CMI_Cross_References.master_customer_id;
